data.description: Very unique condo is ultra modern! Kitchen has 2 dishwashers, 2 refrigerators and 2 freezers, a microwave/convection oven, breakfast bar and plenty of cabinets and workspace. Everything is stainless steel including countertops. Bedroom has nice closet space one being a walk in. You will love the bath with it's unique fixtures, 8 shower heads and heated floors. Kitchen and living area are open and enjoy a beautiful view of the skyline of downtown Little Rock. Also enjoy the view from the balcony. Monthly dues include water, garbage, maintenance, & more.
